00:42:27,430 --> 00:42:40,626
Like in America, in the N.I.H., which is an
Institute for Health, they wanted to test

302
00:42:40,626 --> 00:42:45,015
a sahaja yogi, and there were doctors.

303
00:42:45,015 --> 00:42:49,197
