353
00:48:10,196 --> 00:48:14,418
What is lacking in Sahaja Yoga?

354
00:48:14,443 --> 00:48:16,918
That I have to tell you.

355
00:48:16,973 --> 00:48:23,621
There are so many collective disasters we
have - all kinds of.

